if you do not wish to die!

8
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,480
Professor Hwang, where are you?

9
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:14,080
I think those two will face
a variation in them soon.

10
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:16,120
You have to come quickly. Professor Hwang?

11
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,000
You have my trust.

12
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,840
M, 3, 4.

13
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,320
(Professor Jo Gi-bum)

14
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,240
Tell me.

15
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:33,280
Where did you hide the cryonic...

16
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:35,759
that was here?

17
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,640
I guess...

18
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,280
you've succeeded in thawing them.

19
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,640
Then...

20
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:01,000
who took Lee Seok-du?

21
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,680
Don't kill Professor Hwang.

22
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:22,760
If you do, you'll be done for.

23
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,160
Take him.

24
