is finally going to air.

712
00:55:18,800 --> 00:55:20,000
It's truly a historical moment.

713
00:55:20,200 --> 00:55:21,800
It was planned by Ko Mi-ran...

714
00:55:21,800 --> 00:55:23,400
and directed by Director Ma Dong-chan.

715
00:55:23,960 --> 00:55:27,240
But where is Director Ma?

716
00:55:29,880 --> 00:55:32,080
I saw him working
in the editing room earlier.

717
00:55:32,080 --> 00:55:34,440
