727
00:56:21,600 --> 00:56:23,520
-Yes.
-I'll wait for you.

728
00:56:24,400 --> 00:56:25,840
I'm still very young.

729
00:56:26,320 --> 00:56:28,400
-Don't be such a kid.
-Stop drawing a line.

730
00:56:28,680 --> 00:56:30,320
We're only four years apart.

